Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.51,0:02:01.17,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,止まらない夢を　君と君と　いつか　叶えられるなら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.49,0:02:08.79,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,きっと強くなれる　時をかけるよ今！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.80,0:02:20.60,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,それはPreviousもなく出会う奇跡 Destiny
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.60,0:02:25.94,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,素顔を隠しながら　守るよ　もうひとりじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.40,0:02:31.08,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,わかってるんだずっと　その孤独を
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.44,0:02:36.44,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,Ah...　恐れないで　迷わないで　ありのままで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.87,0:02:41.80,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,約束する　必ず迎えに行く
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.53,0:02:47.23,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,届かない　明日は　高く高く　果てなく
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.43,0:02:53.26,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,目の前にあるReal　願いこの空に消えてく
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.62,0:02:59.17,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,止まらない　夢を　君が君が　いつか　ヒカリ望むなら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.57,0:03:04.89,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,きっとたどり着く　時をかけるよ今！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.17,0:03:10.46,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,君を　君を　君を　守りたいから
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.36,0:03:14.82,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll Be with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.51,0:02:01.17,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,如果将来能和你一起实现那永恒的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.49,0:02:08.79,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定能够变强 现在就穿越时空吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.80,0:02:20.60,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,那是没有预告的奇迹邂逅 是命运
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.60,0:02:25.94,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,戴上面具守护你 再也不会孤单
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.40,0:02:31.08,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直明白你的孤独
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.44,0:02:36.44,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,啊..不要害怕 不要疑惑 做你自己吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.87,0:02:41.80,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,我向你保证 一定会去迎接你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.53,0:02:47.23,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,无法触及的明天 高高在上无穷无尽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.43,0:02:53.26,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,眼前的现实让愿望消散在空中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.62,0:02:59.17,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你在永恒的梦中期盼光明来临的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.57,0:03:04.89,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,你一定会到达那里 现在就穿越时空吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.17,0:03:10.46,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我想要守护你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.36,0:03:14.82,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,我将与你同在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.47,0:22:16.39,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,いつまでもキミの夢も明日(あす)も未来を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.65,0:22:22.13,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,きっと強くなるよ Little*Lion*Heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.53,0:22:35.64,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,気持ちよダッシュして　どんなピンチも追い越せ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.83,0:22:40.99,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,キミを(きっと)すぐに(Soon you feel)もう安心だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.31,0:22:46.46,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,アイマイ弱いハート　限界超えの勇気は
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.70,0:22:52.06,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,いつも(今も)キミの(信号)キャッチ I am ready！！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.45,0:22:56.82,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,誰よりキミが大事だから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.09,0:23:03.13,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,熱くなってく　さあこの心で戦える！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.13,0:23:07.55,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,キミの夢も明日(あす)も未来も
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.85,0:23:13.94,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,この手で絶対守るから　誓ったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.94,0:23:18.34,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,どんな涙も拭いてあげる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.65,0:23:24.38,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,危なっかしいな　でも笑顔でまた困らせて？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.67,0:23:27.27,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,だってだって　まだまだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.27,0:23:29.95,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,小さな勇者は
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.95,0:23:32.55,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,だってだって　もっともっと
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.55,0:23:37.68,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,強くなる Little*Lion*Heart
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.47,0:22:16.39,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,永远守护你的梦想 你的明天 你的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.65,0:22:22.13,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,一定会变得更强大 幼狮雄心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.53,0:22:35.64,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,让心情驰骋起来 超越各种危机
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.83,0:22:40.99,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,一定会马上就让你觉得安心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.31,0:22:46.46,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,暧昧弱小的心需要超越极限的勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.70,0:22:52.06,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,随时都能捕捉到你的信号 我准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.45,0:22:56.82,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,因为比谁都在乎你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.09,0:23:03.13,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,热情不断高涨 来吧 用这个心情去战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.13,0:23:07.55,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,你的梦想 你的明天 你的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.85,0:23:13.94,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,我发誓一定用这双手来守护
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.94,0:23:18.34,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,帮你拭去所有的泪水
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.65,0:23:24.38,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,看着好担心啊 但是你的笑容又让人不知所措
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.67,0:23:27.27,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,因为因为 还没结束
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.27,0:23:29.95,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,小小的勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.95,0:23:32.55,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,因为因为 要变得
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.55,0:23:37.68,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,更强更强 幼狮雄心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.87,0:00:25.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.27,0:00:46.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肚子饿了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.86,0:00:49.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.31,0:01:37.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有受伤吧？女士
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.76,0:01:45.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,英雄 我的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.08,0:03:21.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明明只想过普通的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.23,0:03:36.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以现世骑士团 东亚区馆馆长骑士孙大妃之名
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.66,0:03:41.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在此封花房叶太郎为骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.01,0:03:43.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现世骑士团
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.05,0:03:46.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以创设至今900年以上的悠久历史为豪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.30,0:03:49.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个享有国家地位的主权团体
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.64,0:03:53.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是受到众多国家认可的国际骑士组织
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.69,0:03:57.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直至现代 仍有超过一万人的骑士们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.17,0:04:00.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正在为陷于苦难中的人们而伸出援助之手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.46,0:04:12.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看上去不怎么高兴呢 叶太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.52,0:04:13.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.69,0:04:15.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 森那个家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.53,0:04:17.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次又到哪里闲逛去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.15,0:04:20.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的父亲真是个绝情的家伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.15,0:04:23.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明今天是独生子的披甲仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.82,0:04:25.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花房森
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.09,0:04:28.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,数百年未见的神圣之枪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.48,0:04:31.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被选为先锋之枪的骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.20,0:04:34.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成为了在世传说的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.44,0:04:36.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是我的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.94,0:04:41.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉 反正那家伙的放浪性子也不是今天才养成的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.16,0:04:43.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.73,0:04:45.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.81,0:04:46.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,面具啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.37,0:04:49.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和给多尔衮做的一样 是我的自信之作哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.71,0:04:52.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟你们就像兄弟一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.81,0:04:54.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十分感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.51,0:04:58.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么你怎么打算？那个学园的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.26,0:05:00.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然跟我没什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.45,0:05:04.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底去是不去 由你决定就好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.85,0:05:09.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明明只想过普通的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.38,0:05:17.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好..好痛 请你放手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.64,0:05:21.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么关系 稍微陪我们一下嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.07,0:05:23.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我们一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.82,0:05:24.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我..我不愿意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.23,0:05:26.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这位姐姐是高中生？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.08,0:05:29.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的制服 是森罗学园的对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.95,0:05:31.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和你们没关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.78,0:05:33.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说得这么绝情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.03,0:05:35.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快放开她的手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.38,0:05:41.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把你肮脏的手从女士身上拿开
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.60,0:05:45.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扮得这么夸张 是在玩扮英雄游戏么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.49,0:05:49.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请立刻把你的手从女士身上拿开
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.66,0:05:54.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然的话 我就用这柄枪与你等决一雌雄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.46,0:06:03.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们的选择很明智
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.19,0:06:07.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有受伤吧？女士
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.05,0:06:09.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不..不
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.53,0:06:11.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听到你那撕心裂肺的悲鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.79,0:06:14.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的心也好似被撕裂了一般
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.82,0:06:17.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么没能陪在你的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.25,0:06:22.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会让你遇上那样的暴徒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.64,0:06:26.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请务必接受愚钝的我的赎罪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.49,0:06:31.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身为骑士 我发誓我会永远保护你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.20,0:06:42.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女士？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.34,0:06:45.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变..变态！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.18,0:06:48.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变..变态？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.63,0:06:52.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,“会下意识地以骑士的风格行事”
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.22,0:06:54.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把自己的这种体质..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.52,0:06:58.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,称为骑士道体质
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.53,0:07:03.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从小就接受教育要成为骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.54,0:07:07.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以至于身体会自动做出身为骑士的反应
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.96,0:07:17.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肚子饿了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.81,0:07:28.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油啊 白姬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.74,0:07:32.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能嗅出叶太郎大人味道的只有白姬了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.75,0:07:33.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何啊？白姬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.98,0:07:35.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接近了吗？白姬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.42,0:07:36.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道什么了吗？白姬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.21,0:07:38.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请加油 白姬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.25,0:07:47.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.22,0:07:52.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为 爱丽丝很烦人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.35,0:07:55.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白姬 又不是爱丽丝的马
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.02,0:07:57.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这有什么关系啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.27,0:08:01.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好嗅出叶太郎大人的味道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.57,0:08:03.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白姬已经累了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.88,0:08:05.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝来干就好了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.56,0:08:09.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是马 分辨不出什么味道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.11,0:08:11.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,认真起来的话就能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.61,0:08:12.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.62,0:08:13.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做得到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.59,0:08:14.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.45,0:08:15.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做得到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.21,0:08:16.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.78,0:08:20.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马和..金发美少女？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.92,0:08:17.57,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.15,0:08:18.94,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.98,0:08:20.58,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.35,0:08:22.22,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.18,0:08:22.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝小姐 白姬小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.75,0:08:27.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁允许你们这么胡闹的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.86,0:08:31.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走吧 白姬
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.86,0:08:32.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我..我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.77,0:08:35.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叶太郎大人 您在哪啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.51,0:08:36.53,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,你去哪啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.53,0:08:37.95,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 在那里吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.95,0:08:39.82,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,不 也可能是在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.25,0:08:43.72,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,叶太郎大人 你在吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.74,0:08:41.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女..女仆？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.60,0:08:47.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请原谅我 女士
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.23,0:08:50.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我刚才如果能更早赶来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.29,0:08:54.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就不会让你遭遇如此可怕的经历了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.24,0:08:56.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 女士
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.58,0:08:58.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请给予我下一个机会
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.63,0:09:02.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果下次你再次陷入危机之中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.88,0:09:04.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便是从地球的另一端..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.29,0:09:08.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要为了阻止危机而赶来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.99,0:09:17.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.93,0:09:24.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,英雄..KnightLancer
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.55,0:09:39.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又干傻事了..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.73,0:09:41.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明不想成为骑士的说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.02,0:09:43.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么身体总会做出反应呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.69,0:09:45.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,KnightLancer
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.59,0:09:49.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？不是KnightLancer
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.32,0:09:52.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,KnightLancer？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.99,0:09:53.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.87,0:09:55.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,头戴闪亮面具
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.47,0:09:56.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身披宽大斗篷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.31,0:09:58.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优雅操控巨枪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.13,0:10:00.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拯救受困之人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.31,0:10:02.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后飒爽离开
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.21,0:10:07.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他就是这样的正义英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.09,0:10:09.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正义英雄..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.68,0:10:19.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 来我家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.24,0:10:22.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你肚子饿了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.84,0:10:24.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 这太不好意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.64,0:10:27.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然让今天刚认识的人这么热情相待..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.97,0:10:29.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明连名字都还不知道的说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.04,0:10:32.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你叫什么名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.34,0:10:33.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.56,0:10:37.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫..花房叶太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.18,0:10:39.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叶太郎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.68,0:10:42.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叶子的叶 太郎的太郎 叶太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.97,0:10:46.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叶太郎 很棒的名字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.57,0:10:50.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 你的名字呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.55,0:10:51.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.19,0:10:55.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真绪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.99,0:10:59.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的名字叫鬼堂院真绪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.77,0:11:04.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很美的名字呢 真绪酱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.32,0:11:07.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是真绪酱 是真绪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.20,0:11:13.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是啊 真绪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.89,0:11:36.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办..这样下去的话..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.19,0:11:38.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.47,0:11:39.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真绪大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.41,0:11:45.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧 不要客气
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.52,0:11:48.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真绪大人 欢迎您回来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.16,0:11:50.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您回来的真晚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.99,0:11:52.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了 羽花
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.52,0:11:53.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打..打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.86,0:11:58.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真绪大人 那个..这位是？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.85,0:11:59.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是叶太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.36,0:12:02.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初次见面 我是花房叶太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.27,0:12:04.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我..我是刘羽花
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.55,0:12:08.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是真绪大人的宅子里的女仆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.04,0:12:12.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羽花 晚餐能不能帮叶太郎多准备一份
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.07,0:12:14.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.91,0:12:18.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再把叶太郎的事情跟其他女仆知会一声
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.47,0:12:24.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 其他女仆的勤务时间已结束
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.73,0:12:26.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以大家都回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.57,0:12:29.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.74,0:12:32.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 能麻烦羽花一个人帮我们准备吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.26,0:12:33.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然可以
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.51,0:12:38.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还要请你准备客房和洗澡水
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.86,0:12:40.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊..这？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.56,0:12:42.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会住下吧？叶太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.84,0:12:56.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样行吗？让初识的女生这么照顾我..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.71,0:13:01.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲 父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.74,0:13:05.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叶太郎 叶太郎要变强哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.80,0:13:08.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后保护好公主
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.31,0:13:11.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公主是什么？父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.61,0:13:14.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有朝一日叶太郎会成为强大的骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.26,0:13:17.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会等待着那一天的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.87,0:13:20.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 父亲 父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.50,0:13:27.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是梦啊..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.28,0:13:32.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为..为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.32,0:13:40.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好 叶太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.13,0:13:47.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真绪大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.59,0:13:49.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为..为什么你会在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.42,0:13:50.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？我不可以待在这吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.19,0:13:52.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怕叶太郎会寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.06,0:13:54.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以陪你一起睡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.52,0:13:58.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好 羽花
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.83,0:13:59.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天来得很早呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.01,0:14:00.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 这是..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.19,0:14:03.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明为了不让事情变成这样而留宿了说..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.42,0:14:05.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你住下了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.73,0:14:08.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 羽花也来一起睡就好了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.87,0:14:11.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不光是真绪大人 还想对我下毒手？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.64,0:14:13.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 不 这是..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.94,0:14:17.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不..不 别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.64,0:14:19.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鬼堂院财阀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.93,0:14:23.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拥有悠久历史的名门一族
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.85,0:14:27.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这几年其规模迅速壮大
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.14,0:14:31.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而这孩子便是这个鬼堂院家的独生女
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.00,0:14:34.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些事是羽花小姐告诉我的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.84,0:14:38.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃吗？叶太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.07,0:14:41.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 非常好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.52,0:14:43.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 那太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.65,0:14:48.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很久没有跟别人一起吃饭了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.16,0:14:50.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真绪大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.13,0:14:55.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,午餐和晚餐像往常一样都准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.59,0:14:57.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这位客人的份也准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.14,0:14:59.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.01,0:15:02.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,饭后的收拾已经吩咐羽花了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.92,0:15:03.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.11,0:15:06.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 我们就此告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.81,0:15:08.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦大家了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.41,0:15:16.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些人要回去了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.98,0:15:19.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,工作结束的话当然要回去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.72,0:15:24.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 从昨天开始我就很奇怪..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.05,0:15:27.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里似乎没什么人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.41,0:15:30.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟住在这里的只有我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.40,0:15:33.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？你的父母呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.61,0:15:35.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都还没跟他们打过招呼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.79,0:15:37.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲没有跟我住在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.64,0:15:40.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我的母亲..已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.17,0:15:44.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢款待
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.70,0:15:48.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请..请问
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.75,0:15:49.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真绪..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.91,0:15:55.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真绪小姐她真的是一个人住在这里吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.81,0:15:59.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个..没有人陪她一起住吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.55,0:16:02.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们这里有个规矩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.77,0:16:04.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以和真绪大人太过亲近
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.55,0:16:08.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以和真绪大人一起生活
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.08,0:16:10.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么这样..让这么小的孩子独自一人..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.43,0:16:12.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.41,0:16:14.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然知道为什么还..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.34,0:16:16.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不能违反规矩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.79,0:16:19.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么规矩..这太奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.41,0:16:22.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子的父亲应该也会觉得奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.36,0:16:27.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难不成..这个规矩..就是她父亲..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.37,0:16:31.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真绪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.66,0:16:34.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叶太郎 我说那个..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.00,0:16:37.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能不能来一下我的房间？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.10,0:16:40.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真..真绪大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.08,0:16:44.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叶太郎的话..让他看也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.00,0:16:47.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个人搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.89,0:16:51.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这么突然冒了出来 还千般讨好真绪大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.58,0:16:55.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难不成这个人 是组织的..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.62,0:16:59.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是飞天超人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.06,0:17:02.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是在空中飞翔战斗的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.76,0:17:06.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有还有 这是三眼超人和特锡安
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.14,0:17:08.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三眼超人？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.12,0:17:10.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.55,0:17:12.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 英雄很厉害的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.54,0:17:16.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,英雄很强大 英雄不会输
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.81,0:17:19.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,英雄不会气馁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.05,0:17:24.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天我终于遇到了真正的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.26,0:17:26.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真正的？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.73,0:17:28.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是KnightLancer
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.65,0:17:30.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,KnightLancer？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.36,0:17:33.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.62,0:17:36.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说KnightLancer这个名字是从哪来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.78,0:17:42.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去看看情况 真绪就待在这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.50,0:17:43.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.82,0:17:46.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这算什么..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.56,0:17:48.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是毫无防备呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.61,0:17:51.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.69,0:17:53.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把鬼堂院的丫头交出来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.47,0:17:54.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？你是？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.91,0:17:56.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刘羽花
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.41,0:18:00.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 这里也有我辈之人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.82,0:18:04.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你来的正好 帮我们掳走这丫头
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.42,0:18:05.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我..我拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.20,0:18:07.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们只能用强了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.04,0:18:10.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叶太郎大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.75,0:18:11.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你们回去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.69,0:18:21.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叶太郎大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.01,0:18:23.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下没妨碍了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.83,0:18:26.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不准欺负羽花
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.74,0:18:27.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真绪大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.19,0:18:28.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.19,0:18:34.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓住你了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.88,0:18:36.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,英雄很强大
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.95,0:18:38.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,英雄不会输
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.87,0:18:40.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,英雄不会气馁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.82,0:18:42.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,英雄？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.06,0:18:45.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪有那种东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.86,0:18:55.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,KnightLancer
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.71,0:18:58.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙搞什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.39,0:19:01.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无须担心 女士
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.28,0:19:07.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长枪？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.06,0:19:09.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现世骑士团么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.90,0:19:14.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恣意伤人暴虐无度 像这样的邪恶..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.00,0:19:16.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能容忍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.96,0:19:19.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啰哩啰唆烦死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.75,0:19:53.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.45,0:20:01.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.36,0:20:04.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种破枪 看我把它弄折了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.70,0:20:05.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,KnightLancer
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.88,0:20:07.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾经的骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.53,0:20:11.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身披铁甲降临战场
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.86,0:20:15.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而背负着更沉重之荣耀与使命而战的现世骑士..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.22,0:20:17.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不可能输的！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.01,0:20:33.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.99,0:20:35.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作一点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.56,0:20:39.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想再让女士看到肮脏的血 速速离开
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.75,0:20:41.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.31,0:20:54.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有受伤吧？女士
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.54,0:21:06.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到了吗？羽花
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.84,0:21:08.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是KnightLancer
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.87,0:21:10.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是真正的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.17,0:21:13.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骑士..和父亲一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.19,0:21:16.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,动作快
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.71,0:21:22.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？白姬？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.24,0:21:30.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉 那个出现时机..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.73,0:21:33.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的身份一定暴露了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.81,0:21:38.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很久没有跟别人一起吃饭了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.66,0:21:41.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叶太郎大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.26,0:21:44.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羽花小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.64,0:21:47.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个..您的同伴在等您
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.03,0:21:50.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的..同伴？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.08,0:21:52.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叶太郎大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.97,0:21:55.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么突然就离开了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.99,0:21:58.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可担心您了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.72,0:22:04.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回来 叶太郎先生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.00,0:22:06.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,依子..小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.88,0:22:09.86,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,525)}真正的骑士（英雄）是也
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.43,0:23:41.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本周的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.30,0:23:42.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最热门假面
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.54,0:23:44.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 本周第一个明信片是？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.43,0:23:46.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,六岁的鬼堂院真绪所画
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.15,0:23:47.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 好棒的画呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.50,0:23:50.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她画的是在山中特训时所遇到的真正的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.70,0:23:52.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特别感动的她就把一切画成插画寄了过来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.55,0:23:54.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真绪酱 感谢你的参与
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.18,0:23:55.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么下回的枪与假面舞会
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.97,0:23:57.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叶太郎大危机
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.32,0:23:59.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而爱丽丝果然很逊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.11,0:24:00.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是有在加油了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.91,0:24:02.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 可是没出成果啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.78,0:24:06.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以呢 枪与假面舞会 敬请期待下集
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.07,0:24:08.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 敬..敬请..
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.21,0:24:09.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然好逊哦
